{"tid":398332,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人係澳洲Sydney留學？","createTime":"2017-09-13T06:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T13:33:58.000Z","uid":113697,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e64d7bd0df50985ced9c1bf3ac6d670657a6a005","tid":398332,"uid":113697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:17:52.000Z","msg":"我係UTS讀緊Nursing, 你呢？<br />\n<br />\n知唔知邊道有大大間華人超市？(除左centre 個間人人超市）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d83236c8a3ea465e36e25cdbada82b3897c55cc","tid":398332,"uid":116831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"有華人嘅地方 就有華人超市<br />\n<br />\n不如你同我講 sydney邊度冇華人<br />\n<br />\n其實冇需要 去華人超市買野， UTS library 間Woolworths 夠做啦"},{"pid":"6e44c25d922725d49db66857f171c50f130927fa","tid":398332,"uid":113697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有華人嘅地方 就有華人超市<br />\n<br />\n不如你同我講 sydney邊度冇華人<br />\n<br />\n其實冇需要 去華人超市買野， UTS library 間Woolworths 夠做啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時有去開Woolworths買野，但佢地好少亞洲食物賣或貴，周圍都有華人超市，但想買D日本食品，例如餃子汁，燒汁個D。有無邊間華人超市平得過centre個間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15446d79b1c8f9e3309996fc1eeeb2b2c589ef75","tid":398332,"uid":132949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有華人嘅地方 就有華人超市<br />\n<br />\n不如你同我講 sydney邊度冇華人<br />\n<br />\n其實冇需要 去華人超市買野， UTS library 間Woolworths 夠做啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時有去開Woolworths買野，但佢地好少亞洲食物賣或貴，周圍都有華人超市，但想買D日本食品，例如餃子汁，燒汁個D。有無邊間華人超市平得過centre個間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你去第二間買車錢都大過差價啦"},{"pid":"14f4aff6bdbfab1787f8d718a243a14f8de257ab","tid":398332,"uid":116831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有華人嘅地方 就有華人超市<br />\n<br />\n不如你同我講 sydney邊度冇華人<br />\n<br />\n其實冇需要 去華人超市買野， UTS library 間Woolworths 夠做啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時有去開Woolworths買野，但佢地好少亞洲食物賣或貴，周圍都有華人超市，但想買D日本食品，例如餃子汁，燒汁個D。有無邊間華人超市平得過centre個間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n日本野 去daiso <br />\nCentral / central park 分店<br />\n<br />\n自己格價 有機會貴過華人超市"},{"pid":"963e56b3a031bbec85538f4a7ab74ba2e33ebae8","tid":398332,"uid":90716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"world square 附近有好多日本韓國餐廳同超市"},{"pid":"7ef7311593415fd39015cfc5b8277cb97aad6eeb","tid":398332,"uid":25971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>world square 附近有好多日本韓國餐廳同超市</blockquote><br />\n後面條街有兩間韓國雜貨鋪都幾多野賣"},{"pid":"23f2aff4a695ee92b07ea0511d981fded8ed1030","tid":398332,"uid":127095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:25:37.000Z","msg":"人人超市其實已經算最平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係UTS架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bad83370fc55b28c861ae2ee096d2a0f1a7ee99","tid":398332,"uid":113697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T00:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人人超市其實已經算最平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係UTS架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你住邊區?"},{"pid":"2e6f489bc73a1f5c76507a769747d6d057998ce2","tid":398332,"uid":81552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"華人野唔係人人就通利架啦😂😂😂，遠啲就要起market city個間⋯btw UTS JJ same here"},{"pid":"4c0b6600e5232e3adb05b020b575856d8b61e495","tid":398332,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:31:58.000Z","msg":"好想去u of sydney讀MD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8121edfbc7d26ad51f8f55fca2caf84f40703a1","tid":398332,"uid":113697,"like":0,"dislik